column4: Hi there Guys can someone please help me fix this please I am getting this error on boot 'kinit: no resume image, doing normal boot'  ?
is this a bug can it be fixed 'kinit: no resume image, doing normal boot'  ?
sounds like something is broke, whats the last program you installed/removed/disabled
I did a apt-get install KDE
dark, are you in the directory of the file you want to move?
dark what is the path to the source file?
marko do you have medibuntu enabled?
marko, google medibuntu, the web page will show you how to install the repository, then mPlayer should download what it needs.
do think a reinstall  initramfs-tools will fix 'kinit: no resume image, doing normal boot'
